               <p>Fifth Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
               <p>38. 
               
                  <persName id="t18321129-37-defend442" type="defendantName">
                     ABRAHAM 
                     FRANCIS
                  <interp inst="t18321129-37-defend442" type="surname" value="FRANCIS"></interp>
