             was indicted for <rs id="t18321129-37-off216" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18321129-37-off216" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18321129-37-off216" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18321129-37-cd217" type="crimeDate">30th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-37-off216 t18321129-37-cd217"></join>, 1 pair of shoes, value 18d., and 1 handkerchief, value 1s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18321129-37-victim444" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Valler
                  <interp inst="t18321129-37-victim444" type="surname" value="Valler"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18321129-37-victim444" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
